'''Mary-Angela Tribbiani''' is one of [[Joey Tribbiani|Joey]]'s younger [[Tribbiani Sisters|sisters]] that [[Chandler Bing|Chandler]] fools around with while drunk. And he can't remember which one of the sisters he did it with (in [[The One Where Chandler Can't Remember Which Sister]]).

Mary-Angela was portrayed by [[Holly Gagnier]].
